Package mru.store.model

Class Animals

java.lang.Object
mru.store.model.Toys
mru.store.model.Animals
public class Animals extends mru.store.model.Toys
The Animals class is a subclass of the Toys class and represents a type of toy that is an animal. It contains information such as the serial number, name, brand, price, stock count, minimum age, material, and size.
Version:
6.9
Author:
Caesar and Steven

  • Constructor Details

    • Animals

      public Animals(long serialNum, String name, String brand, float price, int stockCount, int minAge, String material, String size)
      Creates a new animal toy with the specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      serialNum - the serial number of the animal toy
      name - the name of the animal toy
      brand - the brand of the animal toy
      price - the price of the animal toy
      stockCount - the number of animal toys in stock
      minAge - the minimum age that the animal toy is appropriate for
      material - the material that the animal toy is made of
      size - the size of the animal toy
